original_title: PFL Finals 2019 - PFL 10: Harrison vs Pacheco
overview: The PFL 10 mixed martial arts event for the 2019 season of the Professional Fighters League, the 2019 PFL Championship, was held on December 31, 2019, at the Hulu Theater at Madison Square Garden in New York City, New York.
title: PFL Finals 2019 - PFL 10: Harrison vs Pacheco
